<p>
“We have planned a trip to Shilong, haven’t Alisha told you ?”
Deepak was surprised that she didn’t know about the trip.
</p>

<p>
“I know, I mean we two” said Neena.
</p>

<p>
“Oh, where should we go ?” said Deepak.
</p>

<p>
